	<h1 class="title">旧手机别扔了，说不定还能像这些“科技古董”那样卖个好价钱</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113378/small/113378.jpg?1435590009" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">周韶宏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-27 13:27:41 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16650/medium/16650.jpg?1445920568" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16650" data-title="《旧手机别扔了，说不定还能像这些“科技古董”那样卖个好价钱》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16650/medium/16650.jpg?1445920568" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16650.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
